{"type":"text","timestamp":1781151922212,"sessionID":"ses_14b140818ffeCXPWPVn2SL18QY","part":{"id":"prt_eb4ed69dd001oVNDMD14Cp0YU6","messageID":"msg_eb4ed5991001t1HvcWseTpDPWw","sessionID":"ses_14b140818ffeCXPWPVn2SL18QY","type":"text","text":"The code review is now on the implementation path. One notable risk area is incremental packed-index updates after `finalizePackedPostings()`, so I’m checking that path and the FTS5 comparison semantics before writing findings.","time":{"start":1781151918557,"end":1781151922209},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_00211abb050d3ace016a2a38ae8c288191a678c2d81c321c67","phase":"commentary"}}}}
